<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff5f5, #ffeaea);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 5rem;
        margin: 0;
        color: #e63946;
        font-weight: 700;
    }
    p {
        color: #555;
        margin: 10px 0 25px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    a {
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        background: #e63946;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
    }
    a:hover {
        background: #d62839;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.5);
    }
    /* Floating blood drops */
    .drop {
        position: absolute;
        width: 20px;
        height: 30px;
        background: #e63946;
        border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 50% / 60% 60% 40% 40%;
        opacity: 0.2;
        animation: float 6s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    .drop:nth-child(1) { top: 20px; left: 40px; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .drop:nth-child(2) { top: 50px; right: 50px; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
    .drop:nth-child(3) { bottom: 40px; left: 80px; animation-delay: 3s; }
    .drop:nth-child(4) { bottom: 30px; right: 60px; animation-delay: 4.5s; }
    @keyframes float {
        0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.2; }
        50% { transform: translateY(-15px); opacity: 0.4; }
        100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.2; }
    }
</style>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="drop"></div>
        <div class="drop"></div>
        <div class="drop"></div>
        <div class="drop"></div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Oops! Looks like you took a wrong turn.<br>Let’s get you back to saving lives ❤️</p>
        <a href="javascript:history.back()">Go Back</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
